{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was winter time, kind of got clogged up on that wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, and you could, always, even break a leg, you know, because it was going this and that way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I didn't like this, [INAUDIBLE] when she was working night shift.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I gave-- she was wearing my combat boots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took her wooden shoes for the night, because I did not need them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's [INAUDIBLE] shows the two-- two things for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So and then--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is when the-- the war was starting to come close up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was later, then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was already before, you know, in-- in February.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In February when the-- the front was kind of-- I don't know who was going to Ravensbruck, the Russians or the Americans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- from Ravensbruck-- from Ravensbruck, you know, they came a lot of girls, from there, and probably from other things, where we didn't have the-- to accommodate them, the barracks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came frozen, because they marched, too-- the death march.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Guben.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there they were hanging-- at that time, I was not washing, already, the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took me into the kitchen, already, to help out, because they had to feed more, you know, whatever they were-- a little bit of some more soups.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wasn't-- they assigned me to bring in-- you know, there was like, almost like this room, but full of potatoes-- to bring in with baskets, from the kitchen, to put them into that things.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't finish the bag of potatoes, was what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once I exactly put into those things, and I wanted to say, for [INAUDIBLE], that I had to go to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
